ingredientsDesc:
1.I125 Insulin：13mL, Containing Insulin labeled with I125, freeze-dried in phosphate buffer with sodium azide.
2.Insulin Calibrators：CAL0：2mL；CAL 1-6：1mL each. Containing protein solution, sodium azide and Insulin freeze-dried.
3.Insulin Antiserum：12.5mL, Containing anti Insulin serum raised in guinea pig, freeze-dried in phosphate buffer with sodium azide.
4.Insulin Diluent：12.5mL, Containing Insulin free serum freeze-dried with sodium azide.
5.Serotest M：1mL, Containing human serum, freeze-dried with sodium azide.
6.20% TW PEG Solution：125mL.
